{
  "name": "Greater Restoration",
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You imbue a creature you touch with positive energy to undo a debilitating effect. You can reduce the target's Exhaustion level by one, or end one of the following Effects on the target:</p><ul><li>One effect that Charmed, Petrified, possessed (in Materia), or weakened (in Materia) the target</li><li>One curse, including the target's Attunement to a cursed magic item</li><li>Any reduction to one of the target's Ability Scores</li><li>One effect reducing the target's hit point maximum</li></ul><p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 6th level or 7th level, the range is increases to 30 feet instead.</p><p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 8th level or higher, the range is increases to 60 feet instead.</p>",
